title: My Data Science Portfolio
text:
Hi! My name is Rabin, and this is my personal website. As a student in the Master of Data Science program, I’m excited to share my journey and projects here.
I am particularly passionate about applying data science and analytics to the sports industry, using data to uncover new insights and improve performance.
Feel free to look around and learn more about my work!
